1. \(x + y - z = 0.76\)  
2. \(z - y = -0.13\)  

From equation 2, \(z = y - 0.13\). Substitute into equation 1:  
\[x + y - (y - 0.13) = 0.76\]  
\[x + y - y + 0.13 = 0.76\]  
\[x + 0.13 = 0.76\]  
\[x = 0.76 - 0.13 = 0.63\]  

Thus, \(P(A) = 0.63\).  

Verification:  
